AFS0011[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Written evidence submitted by the Kemnal Academies Trust (TKAT)[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Education Select Committee – Inquiry into Academies and Free Schools.[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Executive Summary[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
